OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781359875
OL,3,CYear 13 pupils and university freshers
OL,4,Cto get meningitis jabs on NHS
OL,6,FYear 13 pupils and young people
OL,7,Fstarting university will be offered
OL,8,Fthe Meningitis B (menB) vaccine, after
OL,9,Fa series of outbreaks left two Kent
OL,10,Fteenagers dead.
OL,12,FThe government has announced a one off
OL,13,Fjab programme, which will offer two
OL,14,Fdoses to youngsters aged 17 to 18 in
OL,15,FYear 13, plus those aged under 25
OL,16,Fgoing to university or other
OL,17,Fresidential further education this
OL,18,Fautumn.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
