FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781359875
OL,3,CYear 13 pupils and university freshers
OL,4,Cto get meningitis jabs on NHS
OL,6,FYoung people will be offered their
OL,7,Ffirst dose from July, with a second
OL,8,Fjab given in August.
OL,10,FTwo doses, at least four weeks apart,
OL,11,Fare needed for full protection.
OL,13,FInternational students under the age
OL,14,Fof 25 entering their first year of
OL,15,Funiversity this year, should receive
OL,16,Ftheir first menB dose in their home
OL,17,Fcountry where possible, the Department
OL,18,Fof Health said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
