OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781359875
OL,3,CYear 13 pupils and university freshers
OL,4,Cto get meningitis jabs on NHS
OL,6,FPupils in Year 13 will be contacted
OL,7,Fvia the NHS app, text or letter to
OL,8,Fcome forward for the jab, while others
OL,9,Funder the age of 25 will book their
OL,10,Fappointment directly with pharmacies.
OL,12,FAnyone who misses out on the second
OL,13,FAugust jab because of holidays will
OL,14,Fstill be able to get a jab in
OL,15,FSeptember.
OL,17,FThe roll out comes after a spate of
OL,18,Foutbreaks of meningitis, with the most
OL,19,Fserious being in Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
