PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781359875
OL,3,CYear 13 pupils and university freshers
OL,4,Cto get meningitis jabs on NHS
OL,6,FEighteen-year-old, Juliette Kenny,
OL,7,Fdied in the Kent outbreak earlier this
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FHer family have been campaigning for
OL,11,Fteenagers and young people to be
OL,12,Froutinely given access to the menB
OL,13,Fvaccine ever since.
OL,15,FThe Kent outbreak was the fastest
OL,16,Fgrowing and largest ever seen in the
OL,17,FUK.
OL,19,FOther, smaller clusters of meningitis
OL,20,Fin young people since then have also
OL,21,Fbeen bigger than expected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781359875
OL,3,CYear 13 pupils and university freshers
OL,4,Cto get meningitis jabs on NHS
OL,6,FClose and prolonged contact in halls
OL,7,Fof residence, shared homes and at
OL,8,Fsocial events can increase the risk of
OL,9,Fcontracting the infection.
OL,11,FHealth Secretary James Murray has
OL,12,Furged all eligible students to take up
OL,13,Fthe government's offer to "give them
OL,14,Fpeace of mind as they head off to
OL,15,Fcontinue their studies".
OL,17,FAccording to the UK Health Security
OL,18,FAgency (UKHSA), the risk of menB in
OL,19,Ffirst year university students is
OL,20,Fsubstantially greater than for those
OL,21,Fnot at university.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781359875
OL,3,CYear 13 pupils and university freshers
OL,4,Cto get meningitis jabs on NHS
OL,6,FDr Shamez Ladhani, consultant
OL,7,Fepidemiologist at the UKHSA, said two
OL,8,Fdoses of the menB jab will give "good
OL,9,Fprotection against most strains and
OL,10,Fhelp to give young people and their
OL,11,Ffamilies some reassurance".
OL,13,FCases of invasive disease tend to peak
OL,14,Fin October to November each year.
OL,16,FThe Joint Committee on Vaccination and
OL,17,FImmunisation (JCVI) is currently
OL,18,Fpreparing advice to ministers on
OL,19,Fwhether a bigger and longer programme
OL,20,Fis needed for young people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
