OL,3,CYear 13 pupils and university freshers
OL,4,Cto get meningitis jabs on NHS
OL,6,FWhat are the symptoms of meningitis?
OL,8,FSigns that a person is suffering from
OL,9,Fmeningitis can include, but are not
OL,10,Flimited to, the following, according
OL,11,Fto the NHS:
OL,13,FThe NHS advises people to call 999
OL,14,Fimmediately if you think you or
OL,15,Fsomeone you look after could have
OL,16,Fmeningitis or sepsis.
OL,18,FIt warns that the infection can be
OL,19,Fvery serious if not treated quickly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
